"{\"uid\": \"wnd.com-2024-08-tom-cruise-dives-into-paris-olympics-closing-ceremony-in-jaw-dropping-stunt\", \"text\": \"ByTracy Wright, Fox News  August 11, 2024  (FOX NEWS) - Tom Cruise brought Hollywood to Paris, and back around again.  The \\\"Mission: Impossible\\\" star descended from the top of the Stade de France after H.E.R. sang \\\"The Star-Spangled Banner\\\" during the 2024 Paris Olympics closing ceremony on Sunday, Aug. 11.  IT'S A BIRD. IT'S A PLANE. IT'S TOM CRUISE!#ParisOlympics|#ClosingCeremonypic.twitter.com/5v4j8pOwBF  - NBC Olympics & Paralympics (@NBCOlympics)August 11, 2024    Cameras panned to the top of the building to watch Cruise effortlessly fly through the sky and down to the athletes who competed in the Games of the XXXIII Olympiad.  Read the full story \\u203a  You must belogged into post a comment.  About us  Subscribe  Go Ad-Free  Privacy policy  Copyright \\u00a9 2026 WorldNetDaily  Copyright \\u00a9 2026 WorldNetDaily  March 22, 2026  Joe Kovacs  March 22, 2026  Joe Kovacs  March 22, 2026  RealClearWire\"}"